        "id": "36:0", "name": "Page — Settings", "type": "CANVAS", "backgroundColor": "#060B10",
        "children": [{"id": "36:1", "type": "FRAME", "name": "Settings @ 1440x900", "description": "Sections: Appearance (scheme selector dropdown + 62-swatch 24px grid), Channels (BlueBubbles config / Studio URL / Pi URL / WhatsApp+Discord+Signal off), Brain model (name / host / ctx / fallback chain / temp slider / dry-run toggle), Identity (operator / timezone / locale / currency). Pg-accent = #5A7A90 (scheme #02 pg.settings)."}]
